	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok this is how the 2nd and 3rd part of the quest is done and yes to date so far I have succeeded in doing all of the below and this part is fo the Kata Sha only:<BR>
after you hand in pup claws and cloak you are told to contact Jhimis he is located downstairs from Kaam at bottom of stairs but loc 297, -358, -188.<BR>
                    2nd Part<BR>
(1) After you get your claws and make your straps from rockhoppers and get your note take it to Rittuh Purrik in Hollowshade Moor(inside tents on left inside zone). She will give you a 6 slot bag and ask for 6 Rockhopper tails(ONLY FOUND OFF ROCKHOPPERS IN HOLLOWSHADE MOOR) they look green when looted. when you have 6 combine and give bag back o Rittuh and get an Exagerated Note in return.<BR>
(2) Take exagerated note to Kery Miaan next to KAAM n249, p128, n187 upstairs in same building. you get a carved wooden box to put glowing ore in and your cloak. The glowing ore can be found off Glowing diggers in Paladul caverns. I found glowing diggers in area n2800, -900 just stay to right when you come to water area take right go up and through first opening on right follow path and when you see drop and more water Stay to left Glowing diggers will spawn on left in middle away from water next to mushrooms on ground. I was Lv 15 when i did this and it was tough. Once you get glowing stone put in box with cloak and combine. take back to kerry get cloak back stats as follows: AC6 STR +1 STA +2 HP +5 +2% tailoring. and you get claws.<BR>
(3) Take claws to Kaam in Lib n249, p128, n187 gives you 2 slot bag in which to put 2 molars from sonic pups or wolfling pups from Hollowshade Moor. Note you will need help or stay on road after you go across second bridge stay next to path DO NOT WANDER FAR as sonics will jump you. Hunt Pups and Wolflings till Molars drop. Put in Bag and combine take back to Kaam for Claw mounts for Part 3.<BR>
                    3rd Part<BR>
(1) Ask Jhimis &quot;do you have stretching dowels&quot;<BR>
he will send you to Hollowshade moor and you must get 2 small owlbear claws NOTE these only drop of owlbear  pups if you get other things also needed later like tendons and digested salass moss keep for next part of quest. Once you have two claws and it will take a while i was 3 hours getting em return to Jhimis and hand him two claws AND YOUR CLOAK. in return you will get Stretching dowels. If you fail in stretching the first time you loose the dowels and you  need to do this part again to get dowels.<BR>
<BR>
(2) Buy Weapon Assy kit and all tombs 1 - 3 and read carefully on how to do next part, now it says we have on rely others but I found if we get blacksmithing up to above 50 and make studs then make studded armour after lv 26 till its about 50+ you can succeed in making stretched tendons every time. for the Kata Sha we have the reinforced handwraps(given by kaam) this replaces the ceramic sleeves. here is where you find the parts as all are avail active parts are :<BR>
Salass Moss = Owlbear pup<BR>
Owlbear Tendons = ONLY owlbear pups<BR>
Sonic wolf tendons = sonic wolves<BR>
Kelp salts = Moor tortoise<BR>
Tortoise Saliva = Moor Tortoise<BR>
Fish Oil Soaked Rags = Grimling Fishermen<BR>
Poison dart = Grimling Shamen<BR>
Acrylia Mortor and Pestle = Vendor Mugdah<BR>
n353, p504, n190 near s gate old area Shar Vahl<BR>
Poison vial = vedor alchemist<BR>
Water = Vendors<BR>
Claw Mounts = last part of quest<BR>
<BR>
NOTE: From reading book we dont need ceramice sleeves or porous dagger blade or wolf bane. could be wrong but dont think so.<BR>
<BR>
(3) Take Salass moss, turtle saliva, sonic wolf blood and poison dart put in mortor and pestle and combine<BR>
(4) put mixture in Poison vial and put in kiln or forge and bake<BR>
(5) take mixture and when done add water then keep in inventory till needed later<BR>
(6) Take owlbear tendons and Sonic wolf tendons and stretching dowels and put in Large sewing kit and combine. once stretched add kelp salts and fish oil soaked rags and combine again. NOTE tailoring must be in 50s or this will fail I had to do it 3 times before I got it right.<BR>
(7) take treated tendons and poison mixture and your claw mounts(given by Kaam look like metal gloves in inv) and combine in a weapon assy kit.<BR>
(8) take new claws and your cloak back to Jhimis for reward. I have gotten everything but the poison dart as the shaman keeps kicking my butt.<BR>
<BR>
If anyone has done to completion and I am missing something pls add after as I have done all i can till I get poison dart.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
